 <span data-ttu-id="b3d73-106">实现 <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3d73-106">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="b3d73-107">接收的数组<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>实例，并创建一个新的数组<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment>实例将传递给`Speak`基础的合成引擎上的方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b3d73-107">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
